      "date": "2013-01-29 07:23:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/bf6b201c-69e1-11e2-9da0-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
